WEBVTT

00:00:44.100 --> 00:00:48.700
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

00:00:49.420 --> 00:00:51.780
=Episode 3=

00:00:55.160 --> 00:00:55.800
Grandma, look.

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:58.020
(Letter of Intent)

00:01:02.521 --> 00:01:04.521
Mom, you really need
to read this carefully.

00:01:04.800 --> 00:01:05.921
Don't let them trick you.

00:01:05.921 --> 00:01:06.990
What nonsense are you spouting?

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:08.090
It's all in black and white.

00:01:08.241 --> 00:01:09.601
There's even the Dihao seal on it.

00:01:09.601 --> 00:01:10.561
How could it be fake?

00:01:10.561 --> 00:01:11.360
Enough, all of you!

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:14.160
Churan,

00:01:14.681 --> 00:01:16.360
you did very well this time.

00:01:16.761 --> 00:01:19.160
You truly didn't disappoint
all the years of training

00:01:19.320 --> 00:01:20.440
I gave you.

00:01:20.921 --> 00:01:22.041
Thank you, Grandma.

00:01:22.041 --> 00:01:24.121
But honestly,
this was all thanks to Ye Chen.

00:01:25.320 --> 00:01:27.121
Because of him,
I was able to meet Ms. Wang

00:01:27.121 --> 00:01:29.401
and personally hand her the proposal.

00:01:30.520 --> 00:01:32.041
I merely led her the way.

00:01:32.041 --> 00:01:34.001
The success came
from Churan's brilliance.

00:01:35.320 --> 00:01:36.240
I knew it.

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:37.281
Churan

00:01:37.281 --> 00:01:38.720
is the most exceptional of them all.

00:01:40.440 --> 00:01:42.121
Then congratulations are in order.

00:01:42.561 --> 00:01:44.080
Mr. Zhang has lost.

00:01:44.080 --> 00:01:45.360
That trash Ye Chen

00:01:45.720 --> 00:01:47.401
is your son-in-law forever now.

00:01:50.281 --> 00:01:51.520
Who says I lost?

00:01:54.080 --> 00:01:54.681
Ye Chen,

00:01:55.360 --> 00:01:56.320
a trash like you

00:01:56.320 --> 00:01:57.761
should stop deceiving Churan already!

00:01:58.440 --> 00:01:59.800
(Why is he everywhere?)

00:02:00.121 --> 00:02:01.041
Churan,

00:02:01.720 --> 00:02:04.681
the truth is,
Dihao never liked your proposal.

00:02:04.681 --> 00:02:07.240
I personally went to see Ms. Wang,

00:02:07.440 --> 00:02:09.761
and it was only for the sake
of the Zhang family

00:02:10.001 --> 00:02:12.001
and my reputation that she gave you

00:02:12.001 --> 00:02:13.240
this Letter of Intent.

00:02:13.401 --> 00:02:14.440
Are you out of your mind?

00:02:14.440 --> 00:02:16.121
Wenhao,

00:02:16.320 --> 00:02:18.200
how can you be so biased?

00:02:18.200 --> 00:02:19.681
Sorry about that, sis.

00:02:20.600 --> 00:02:22.640
It's because I love Churan too much.

00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:24.681
Did you hear that, Xiao Churan?

00:02:25.001 --> 00:02:26.241
You don't honestly think

00:02:26.241 --> 00:02:27.950
this was achieved
by your own ability, do you?

00:02:27.961 --> 00:02:29.001
Don't make things up!

00:02:29.121 --> 00:02:31.320
Churan's proposal
was obviously the best.

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:32.281
But of course,

00:02:32.561 --> 00:02:33.841
we should also thank Mr. Zhang.

00:02:34.521 --> 00:02:35.320
Mom!

00:02:35.681 --> 00:02:37.200
You believe everything he says?

00:02:37.600 --> 00:02:39.121
That's simply the truth.

00:02:41.440 --> 00:02:42.440
Zhang Wenhao,

00:02:43.160 --> 00:02:44.720
you've told such a massive lie!

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:47.241
Aren't you worried Ms. Wang
will expose you in person?

00:02:47.880 --> 00:02:49.320
The one exposed will be you.

00:02:49.720 --> 00:02:51.600
Do you dare to raise the stakes

00:02:51.600 --> 00:02:52.390
of our previous bet?

00:02:57.841 --> 00:02:58.760
If you manage

00:02:58.920 --> 00:03:00.521
to bring Ms. Wang,

00:03:00.640 --> 00:03:02.600
then I'll apologize to Churan

00:03:03.001 --> 00:03:03.801
in front of everyone

00:03:04.401 --> 00:03:07.760
and swear never to interfere
in her life again.

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:08.521
Deal!

00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:10.200
But with one more condition.

00:03:10.640 --> 00:03:13.440
Xiao Group must appoint Churan
as the director.

00:03:13.961 --> 00:03:14.880
And if

00:03:14.880 --> 00:03:17.160
Ms. Wang doesn't show up that day?

00:03:20.040 --> 00:03:22.241
I'll leave the Xiao family and Churan

00:03:22.241 --> 00:03:24.720
and kneel in front of you.

00:03:25.001 --> 00:03:25.760
Alright.

00:03:26.121 --> 00:03:27.241
It's a deal.

00:03:27.480 --> 00:03:29.480
If you really manage to bring Ms. Wang,

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:32.760
I'll drop to my knee right there
in front of everyone.

00:03:32.920 --> 00:03:33.760
Okay.

00:03:34.320 --> 00:03:35.760
Remember every word you said today.

00:03:35.920 --> 00:03:37.281
Then it's settled.

00:03:38.440 --> 00:03:39.561
Three days from now,

00:03:39.561 --> 00:03:42.640
I will host a grand signing ceremony.

00:03:43.480 --> 00:03:45.521
If Ms. Wang doesn't appear...

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:46.760
There is no "if".

00:03:53.760 --> 00:03:54.521
Mr. Ye,

00:03:55.121 --> 00:03:56.160
don't worry.

00:03:56.160 --> 00:03:58.281
I will be there three days later.

00:03:59.480 --> 00:04:00.681
Thank you.

00:04:00.681 --> 00:04:02.040
Now that's real loyalty.

00:04:02.760 --> 00:04:03.320
Um...

00:04:03.640 --> 00:04:05.880
There's one more thing
I'd like to trouble you with.

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:11.681
Could you maybe lend me a bit of money?

00:04:11.961 --> 00:04:14.760
I want to get Churan an outfit
for the signing ceremony.

00:04:15.281 --> 00:04:15.841
That way,

00:04:16.320 --> 00:04:18.521
it'll reflect well on her, on me,

00:04:19.320 --> 00:04:20.121
and on all of you.

00:04:20.361 --> 00:04:23.001
Mr. Ye, do you know
Jinzhou's largest commercial street?

00:04:23.561 --> 00:04:24.400
Yes I do.

00:04:24.700 --> 00:04:26.400
I used to deliver food there
all the time.

00:04:26.481 --> 00:04:28.681
That entire street belongs to Dihao.

00:04:28.960 --> 00:04:30.280
Just take Mrs. Ye there

00:04:30.520 --> 00:04:32.041
and pick whatever you want.

00:04:33.001 --> 00:04:34.161
You're serious?

00:04:37.400 --> 00:04:38.721
I don't think that's appropriate.

00:04:38.921 --> 00:04:40.760
Churan still doesn't know
my real identity.

00:04:41.001 --> 00:04:42.161
Let's keep things low-key.

00:04:43.161 --> 00:04:43.921
Low-key please.

00:04:46.561 --> 00:04:47.241
Mr. Ye,

00:04:47.801 --> 00:04:49.080
please take this card first then.

00:04:51.880 --> 00:04:53.200
How much is in it?

00:04:53.440 --> 00:04:55.001
Enough to last you for a while.

00:04:56.880 --> 00:04:57.481
Alright.

00:05:04.280 --> 00:05:05.880
Thank you, Dongxue.

00:05:07.320 --> 00:05:08.601
Then I'm done here.

00:05:09.840 --> 00:05:10.681
I'll get going now.

00:05:11.080 --> 00:05:11.921
Thank you very much.

00:05:12.121 --> 00:05:13.100
No need to walk me out.

00:05:13.280 --> 00:05:14.080
Really, no need.

00:05:14.721 --> 00:05:15.400
No need.

00:05:16.001 --> 00:05:17.121
I'm leaving first.

00:05:19.161 --> 00:05:20.041
Mr. Tang,

00:05:20.320 --> 00:05:21.440
as you predicted,

00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:23.400
Mr. Ye has already taken the bait.

00:05:23.760 --> 00:05:24.400
Continue.

00:05:25.161 --> 00:05:27.121
Let the hook sink deeper.

00:05:27.840 --> 00:05:28.361
Understood.

00:05:28.840 --> 00:05:31.241
I've spent 20 years
setting this game in motion,

00:05:31.640 --> 00:05:33.400
having Elder Quan train him,

00:05:34.120 --> 00:05:36.241
and arranging for him to marry
into the Xiao family.

00:05:36.840 --> 00:05:39.520
If even a word of this leaks...

00:05:39.520 --> 00:05:41.041
This will remain a secret.

00:05:41.121 --> 00:05:42.161
I understand completely.

00:05:43.921 --> 00:05:46.440
It seems the time has come
for him to make his appearance.

00:05:48.300 --> 00:05:50.820
(24-Hour Self-Service ATM)

00:06:04.580 --> 00:06:05.260
(Balance Inquiry)

00:06:08.001 --> 00:06:09.481
Two... three...

00:06:10.080 --> 00:06:11.840
Four... five...

00:06:12.200 --> 00:06:13.640
Six... seven...

00:06:14.561 --> 00:06:15.280
(Ten billion)
Eight...

00:06:28.601 --> 00:06:30.921
(That entire street belongs to Dihao.)

00:06:33.121 --> 00:06:34.520
(All of this... is mine.)

00:06:39.200 --> 00:06:40.721
Do you know who you're messing with?

00:06:48.601 --> 00:06:49.161
Hey, Dakun.

00:06:49.400 --> 00:06:50.190
What are you up to?

00:06:50.601 --> 00:06:51.880
What's wrong, Chen?

00:06:52.161 --> 00:06:52.880
I want to ask you.

00:06:53.300 --> 00:06:55.200
Hypothetically,
if I suddenly had 100 million,

00:06:55.520 --> 00:06:57.121
no wait, ten billion!

00:06:57.500 --> 00:06:58.681
How should I spend that money?

00:06:59.481 --> 00:07:01.520
Did you have too much
to drink yesterday?

00:07:01.520 --> 00:07:02.580
Still not sober, are you?

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:04.080
I'm serious.

00:07:04.640 --> 00:07:05.161
Look.

00:07:05.640 --> 00:07:07.840
From that end of the street,
to the other end there,

00:07:08.100 --> 00:07:08.681
it's all mine.

00:07:09.320 --> 00:07:10.960
Sure. The whole universe is yours too.

00:07:11.161 --> 00:07:12.001
Goal!

00:07:12.640 --> 00:07:13.440
Damn you!

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:15.041
Who's this?

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:16.481
Move aside.

00:07:17.561 --> 00:07:18.681
Who are you talking to?

00:07:18.681 --> 00:07:20.561
Is this where you should be?

00:07:22.400 --> 00:07:23.681
He's just eating by the roadside.

00:07:23.681 --> 00:07:24.990
How is that any of your business?

00:07:25.320 --> 00:07:26.041
Forget it.

00:07:26.041 --> 00:07:26.880
Forget it?

00:07:27.200 --> 00:07:28.280
You've got to be reasonable.

00:07:28.640 --> 00:07:29.481
Just eat here.

00:07:30.801 --> 00:07:32.840
Do you know what place this is?

00:07:32.840 --> 00:07:34.320
Cuixuan Pavilion.

00:07:34.681 --> 00:07:35.561
Get lost now!

00:07:35.960 --> 00:07:36.760
Come on, bro.

00:07:37.161 --> 00:07:37.840
Follow me.

00:07:38.280 --> 00:07:39.280
Step aside!

00:07:39.660 --> 00:07:41.740
(Cuixuan Pavilion)

00:07:43.121 --> 00:07:43.721
Out!

00:07:44.161 --> 00:07:46.681
I told you two to get out,

00:07:47.080 --> 00:07:48.440
not walk in!

00:07:48.440 --> 00:07:49.840
I'm here to spend money.

00:07:49.840 --> 00:07:51.400
Is this how you treat customers?

00:07:51.640 --> 00:07:54.400
You think you can afford
to shop here?

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:55.280
Get lost!

00:07:58.200 --> 00:07:59.200
Come on everybody!

00:07:59.200 --> 00:08:00.041
Take a look!

00:08:00.921 --> 00:08:03.041
Look at this famous brand
humiliating its customers!

00:08:03.050 --> 00:08:04.870
If you can't afford it,
they won't even let you look!

00:08:04.880 --> 00:08:05.990
Bullying us just because they're big!

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:07.520
Manager, so many people are watching.

00:08:07.520 --> 00:08:08.200
This looks bad.

00:08:09.320 --> 00:08:10.280
Film him.

00:08:10.880 --> 00:08:12.361
Just look then!

00:08:12.601 --> 00:08:13.440
Come inside.

00:08:13.601 --> 00:08:15.361
See which one you can afford.

00:08:17.960 --> 00:08:19.481
Which is the most expensive item here?

00:08:20.041 --> 00:08:20.840
This one.

00:08:21.801 --> 00:08:23.280
This is our crown jewel.

00:08:23.400 --> 00:08:24.440
Ultra-A quality.

00:08:24.440 --> 00:08:26.241
It's worth ten million.

00:08:27.320 --> 00:08:27.880
I'll take it.

00:08:28.320 --> 00:08:30.440
If trash like you two could afford that,

00:08:30.440 --> 00:08:31.990
I'd be the world's richest man tomorrow.

00:08:32.320 --> 00:08:33.241
Manager, stop it.

00:08:33.241 --> 00:08:34.320
How long have you worked here?

00:08:34.320 --> 00:08:35.690
You still don't know how to read people.

00:08:35.700 --> 00:08:36.790
Don't bother coming in tomorrow.

00:08:37.880 --> 00:08:39.201
I think this lady

00:08:39.400 --> 00:08:40.961
shouldn't be fired.

00:08:41.420 --> 00:08:43.280
In fact, she deserves a promotion
and a raise.

00:08:43.280 --> 00:08:44.601
Don't lecture me.

00:08:44.760 --> 00:08:48.241
Cuixuan Pavilion
only serves distinguished customers.

00:08:48.241 --> 00:08:49.880
Trash like you should get out.

00:08:49.880 --> 00:08:51.721
How do you know I can't afford it?

00:08:51.721 --> 00:08:52.880
You?

00:08:53.241 --> 00:08:54.520
Who are you?

00:08:55.201 --> 00:08:56.760
Is this enough?

00:08:57.680 --> 00:08:58.640
A black card?

00:09:00.841 --> 00:09:02.961
Symbol of elite status.

00:09:03.721 --> 00:09:04.481
Looks pretty real.

00:09:05.321 --> 00:09:06.280
Where'd you get it made?

00:09:06.481 --> 00:09:08.241
How do you know it's fake? Swipe it.

00:09:08.241 --> 00:09:09.760
Ten million in cash

00:09:09.920 --> 00:09:12.040
if you want to buy our crown jewel.

00:09:14.520 --> 00:09:16.441
Cash withdrawal
at this hour might be difficult.

00:09:16.520 --> 00:09:19.001
If you can't afford it, just say so.

00:09:20.280 --> 00:09:21.800
Bro.

00:09:22.441 --> 00:09:23.321
I've got a way.

00:09:33.081 --> 00:09:34.280
Sorry to trouble you, bro.

00:09:35.481 --> 00:09:36.481
Thank you.

00:09:36.680 --> 00:09:37.201
Thanks.

00:09:37.961 --> 00:09:38.481
Put it here.

00:09:38.600 --> 00:09:39.590
Much appreciated, really.

00:09:39.841 --> 00:09:40.481
Thanks.

00:09:40.481 --> 00:09:41.961
Sir, I'm the store manager.

00:09:41.961 --> 00:09:42.990
I've heard about what happened.

00:09:43.081 --> 00:09:43.920
I'm truly very sorry.

00:09:44.321 --> 00:09:45.160
No need to apologize.

00:09:45.920 --> 00:09:46.880
Just count the money.

00:09:47.100 --> 00:09:48.321
So you won't turn around later

00:09:48.321 --> 00:09:49.880
and say some poor guy shortchanged you.

00:09:50.400 --> 00:09:52.040
Alright, we'll do as you say.

00:09:52.040 --> 00:09:52.841
All as you say.

00:09:52.961 --> 00:09:53.520
Hurry up.

00:09:56.520 --> 00:09:57.441
Wait.

00:09:57.880 --> 00:09:58.640
Count it by hand.

00:09:59.361 --> 00:09:59.841
But...

00:10:00.300 --> 00:10:01.790
If you don't want to count,
that's fine too.

00:10:02.441 --> 00:10:03.241
From now on,

00:10:03.880 --> 00:10:05.481
you are this store's sales manager.

00:10:07.441 --> 00:10:09.481
- Bravo!
- Thank you!

00:10:10.081 --> 00:10:11.961
Good job!

00:10:19.280 --> 00:10:21.160
Wow... it's so beautiful.

00:10:21.400 --> 00:10:22.121
Right?

00:10:22.520 --> 00:10:23.280
Ultra-A quality.

00:10:25.280 --> 00:10:26.560
I still need to thank you.

00:10:27.721 --> 00:10:29.241
No, not the A you're thinking of.

00:10:29.241 --> 00:10:30.560
Not that A.

00:10:30.760 --> 00:10:32.280
I mean the A that means "really good".

00:10:32.280 --> 00:10:34.160
- Like...
- Does it look good?

00:10:35.721 --> 00:10:36.520
Yes, it does.

00:10:38.520 --> 00:10:39.560
From now on,

00:10:39.961 --> 00:10:41.520
(Another rich second-gen)
you are this store's sales manager.

00:10:41.880 --> 00:10:42.920
I've already arranged

00:10:43.040 --> 00:10:45.201
to have all videos of Mr. Ye taken down.

00:10:46.400 --> 00:10:47.081
But,

00:10:47.241 --> 00:10:49.241
his identity
probably can't be hidden anymore.

00:10:51.160 --> 00:10:52.380
It was never going to stay hidden.

00:10:52.601 --> 00:10:54.520
Zhang Wenhao
didn't appear out of nowhere.

00:10:55.241 --> 00:10:57.961
It's time to bring them into the light.

00:10:58.680 --> 00:11:00.640
Won't Mr. Ye be in danger?

00:11:01.121 --> 00:11:03.961
If he can't even deal
with a few small fry like them,

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:05.841
then what use is he to me?

00:11:09.040 --> 00:11:10.160
From now on,

00:11:10.520 --> 00:11:12.361
you are this store's sales manager.

00:11:15.060 --> 00:11:15.460
(Video removed)

00:11:19.920 --> 00:11:20.441
Boss.

00:11:21.081 --> 00:11:23.841
Now that we already know
Ye Chen's connection to Dihao,

00:11:24.081 --> 00:11:25.241
what are you waiting for?

00:11:25.241 --> 00:11:26.441
Rest assured.

00:11:26.680 --> 00:11:27.760
Everything is prepared.

00:11:27.760 --> 00:11:29.880
Ye Chen won't live
to see the signing ceremony.

00:11:30.321 --> 00:11:30.841
Remember.

00:11:31.361 --> 00:11:32.800
What I want is the formula.

00:11:33.280 --> 00:11:34.241
Deal with Xiao Churan.

00:11:34.920 --> 00:11:36.040
Get the formula.

00:11:37.081 --> 00:11:37.961
Understood.

00:11:38.920 --> 00:11:39.800
Ye Chen,

00:11:40.081 --> 00:11:41.680
we'll see who has the last laugh.

00:11:43.321 --> 00:11:45.441
I've waited 20 full years.

00:11:45.441 --> 00:11:46.601
The real show

00:11:47.361 --> 00:11:48.800
is finally about to begin.

00:12:06.420 --> 00:12:08.908
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

00:12:08.995 --> 00:12:12.748
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

00:12:13.208 --> 00:12:18.145
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

00:12:18.308 --> 00:12:20.595
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

00:12:20.908 --> 00:12:23.588
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

00:12:24.658 --> 00:12:27.283
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

00:12:27.583 --> 00:12:30.595
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

00:12:30.795 --> 00:12:33.845
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

00:12:33.958 --> 00:12:36.920
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

00:12:37.188 --> 00:12:40.345
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

00:12:40.570 --> 00:12:44.320
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

00:12:44.320 --> 00:12:47.183
♪I belong to no one♪

00:12:47.245 --> 00:12:50.695
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

00:12:50.695 --> 00:12:53.370
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

00:12:53.370 --> 00:12:59.708
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪